com.thomsonreuters.upa.examples.edfexamples.common

Class EDFDictionaryHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.thomsonreuters.upa.examples.common.DictionaryHandler
      • com.thomsonreuters.upa.examples.edfexamples.common.EDFDictionaryHandler

  • public class EDFDictionaryHandler
extends DictionaryHandler
    This is the dictionary handler for the UPA EDF Consumer application. It provides methods for loading the field/enumType dictionaries from a file and sending requests for those dictionaries and the GlobalSetDef dictionary to the Ref Data Server. Methods for processing the dictionary response and closing a dictionary stream are also provided.
